<plot>A half hour documentary which explores different aspects of the first generation Iranian immigrant experience from the insider's perspective. The film focuses on the younger generation and is a fast paced and very entertaining look at the issues of ethnicity and separation told from the point of view of four dynamic and funny characters, including the actor, Omid Djalili.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087926</url></doc>
